  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334910/extras/61f69a604608e9f5787142c092a50b7e.poster.avif?t=1728841127\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334910/extras/61f69a604608e9f5787142c092a50b7e.webm?t=1728841127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334910/extras/61f69a604608e9f5787142c092a50b7e.mp4?t=1728841127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Snake, slither, SLURRPP!</strong><br>How long can you grow your Space Slurpie? In this relaxing multiplayer game, control a colorful space snake with your hand. Chill out with your friends while collecting as much food as possible. The more you eat, the more the snake grows. Try not to run into other players or all kinds of playful baddies! With a calming Zen mode, multiplayer modifiers, and over 30 solo maps, there is a game mode for everyone to enjoy.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334910/extras/445d71b74f755ee49a30e4f3a2e2fc61.poster.avif?t=1728841127\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334910/extras/445d71b74f755ee49a30e4f3a2e2fc61.webm?t=1728841127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334910/extras/445d71b74f755ee49a30e4f3a2e2fc61.mp4?t=1728841127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Players control a snake that follows your hand<br></li><li>It grows in length as you eat food<br></li><li>Evolve and cover yourself in armor as it grows<br></li><li>Survive the longest without colliding with yourself or other players<br></li><li>Competitive players can sabotage each other to win the game<br></li><li>Avoid the Jazzeroids and other enemy obstacles on your quest to be the longest slurp!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334910/extras/5c78afc33ab262b9e2ca2141383461ec.poster.avif?t=1728841127\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334910/extras/5c78afc33ab262b9e2ca2141383461ec.webm?t=1728841127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334910/extras/5c78afc33ab262b9e2ca2141383461ec.mp4?t=1728841127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoy over 30 unique and vibrant maps<br></li><li>Cross platform multiplayer, both matchmaking and games with friends<br></li><li>Customize your snake and make uniquely yours</li></ul>",
