s<br></li><li>Competitive players can sabotage each other to win the game<br></li><li>Avoid the Jazzeroids and other enemy obstacles on your quest to be the longest slurp!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334910/extras/5c78afc33ab262b9e2ca2141383461ec.poster.avif?t=1728841127\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334910/extras/5c78afc33ab262b9e2ca2141383461ec.webm?t=1728841127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334910/extras/5c78afc33ab262b9e2ca2141383461ec.mp4?t=1728841127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoy over 30 unique and vibrant maps<br></li><li>Cross platform multiplayer, both matchmaking and games with friends<br></li><li>Customize your snake and make uniquely yours</li></ul>",
